[normal]ies
[normal] in relation to the conduct of
[normal] 
[normal]referendums held under the framework of the Political Parties, Elections and Referendums Act 2000 (PPERA). The proposed 
[normal]referendum included within the D
[normal]raft Wales Bill
[normal] will
[normal] be 
[normal]conducted under that framework.
[normal]1.4
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]In any such
[normal] referendum,
[normal] our role includes:
