[normal]New recommendations[bold]1.43
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]During 2011-12 the Commission undertook a review of the of the UK’s party and election finance laws
[normal]. 
[normal]We recommended new measures
[normal] to simplify the registration process, provide more detailed reporting of pre-registration spending, requiring imprints on electronic material and improvements to the workability of the provisions around sanctioning and late payment of fines. We would of c
[normal]ourse be happy to work with the Government to take these new recommendations forward.
